snippet.title: Catherine Classic is now available on PC!
snippet.description: The original ATLUS classic action-adventure puzzler returns! Catherine Classic is available now for the first time on PC with enhancements for modern PC like 4K resolutions, unlocked framerate, customizable keyboard and mouse controls and optional Japanese Voice Over included.
